{"tid":343409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國凍結委內瑞拉馬杜羅資產 禁公民與其交易","createTime":"2017-08-01T12:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T14:17:47.000Z","uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d55dec142bf4c24a2292ee0a3c70ba2bd5c5253f","tid":343409,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"美凍結馬杜羅資產禁公民與其交易 2017/08/01 09:00<br />\n美國宣佈制裁委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅，凍結他在美國的資產，回應馬杜羅發起被指助長總統集權的制憲議會選舉，但委內瑞拉石油業不受影響，馬杜羅批評美國制裁行動非法。 <br />\n<br />\n馬杜羅宣稱周日的制憲議會選舉空前成功，不過多個國家均指選舉違法，美國財政部周一宣佈制裁馬杜羅，姆欽又指委內瑞拉制憲議會的當選人亦可能受到美國制裁，國家安全顧問麥克馬斯特批評馬杜羅獨裁、藉制憲議會攬權。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過美國暫時未有制裁委內瑞拉經濟命脈之一的石油業，華府官員解釋不希望制裁措施對委內瑞拉人民的影響，大於對政府的打擊。選舉過後，首都加拉加斯局勢稍為緩和，街頭布滿示威者和警方衝突後遺下的雜物，有居民批評馬杜羅政府謊話連篇，制憲議會選舉鬧劇一場、缺乏認受性。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n司法部長奧爾特加要求成立委員會徹查選舉，有否削弱委內瑞拉民眾權利，不排除交國際機構仲裁，奧爾特加曾批評立場親政府的最高法院接管國會立法權、破壞憲制秩序。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764a100ec96070489c1737c0b9c7993440d85d2b","tid":343409,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉反對派頭目家中被帶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被帶走時仲著住睡衣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: CNN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2017/08/01/americas/venezuela-election-unrest/index.html?sr=fbCNN080117venezuela-election-unrest0716AMVODtop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2Famericas%2Fvenezuela-election-unrest%2Findex.html%3Fsr%3DfbCNN080117venezuela-election-unrest0716AMVODtop&d=g6HUuDliaoTZmEauGmvtRKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=f4a42218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2Famericas%2Fvenezuela-election-unrest%2Findex.html%3Fsr%3DfbCNN080117venezuela-election-unrest0716AMVODtop&h=46bed64c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://edition.cnn.com/2017/08/01/americas/venezuela-election-unrest/index.html?sr=fbCNN080117venezuela-election-unrest0716AMVODtop</a>"},{"pid":"432abd784763f9fab0d67154d71226374c898cda","tid":343409,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"不過美國暫時未有制裁委內瑞拉經濟命脈之一的石油業，華府官員解釋不希望制裁措施對委內瑞拉人民的影響，大於對政府的打擊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b96d72170d3c954654bdc8b2d7073173808681","tid":343409,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"唔怪得雜種次次外訪都成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}